descriptionHtml:
[size=2]Another small mod with just a bunch of textures.
This mod will affect all armors that will use the FALMER HEAVY textures, including:[/size]
[list]
[*][size=2]all Falmer Heavy Bikinis, by nisetanaka;[/size]
[*][size=2]the Falmer Heavy Remodeled by gamefever;[/size]
[*][size=2]both vanilla Male and Female Falmer Heavy armors;[/size]
[*][size=2]other sexy armors whose creator name I don't recall right now (I've put some screenshots though);[/size]
[*][size=2]the charurus hunter monster.[/size]
[/list]
As always my textures are darker than the original ones - I call this: make them serious. This ones though are particularly dark, because I created them especially for nisetanaka bikinis and I think they look better if they are very dark.

I put screenshots of everything I use. Take a look and decide whether you like them or not. (The vanilla textures are from High Resolution texture pack)
author: Arjuna76
